data.description: This beautiful end unit welcomes you with a fenced yard. Entertainers dream of this open family room & kitchen. Storage galore & extensive granite serving bar and workspace with a walk-in pantry. Sip coffee from the 2nd-floor balcony. 1st floor bedroom with adjoining full bath creates a perfect guest quarters. Over-sized master suite has dual sinks, a separate shower & walk-in closet. Relax in your jetted tub. The secondary bedroom is flexible for use as an office or nursery.
